♪Bold ambition
interspersed with recklessness♪

7
00:00:55,290 --> 00:00:58,520
♪Mind not the predestination♪

8
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:01,540
♪Solving all the problems
that fate presents me♪

9
00:01:01,540 --> 00:01:03,040
♪From all the trials and hardship♪

10
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:04,770
♪Spawn the vast courage♪

11
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:06,520
♪The journey to seek glory and justice♪

12
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,120
♪Is not in vain♪

13
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,840
