583
00:24:19,540 --> 00:24:20,580
In the past,

584
00:24:21,060 --> 00:24:22,660
we could have waited for His Majesty
to make a decision.

585
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,020
But the Sixth Prince, Xiao Chuhe,

586
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:25,900
has shown up.

587
00:24:26,940 --> 00:24:28,060
Everything has changed.

588
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:29,860
I know

589
00:24:31,100 --> 00:24:32,090
that some of you

590
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:33,900
are teachers of Lord Bai,

591
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:35,300
and some of you

592
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:36,660
are loyal followers of Lord Chi.

593
00:24:37,260 --> 00:24:38,060
Xiao Chuhe's presence

594
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:38,860
is the greatest threat

595
00:24:40,100 --> 00:24:41,180
to you.

596
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:44,300
You

597
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,500
shouldn't have told

598
00:24:46,660 --> 00:24:47,620
His Majesty the news

599
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:50,220
without discussing it with us,

600
00:24:50,660 --> 00:24:51,460
and you shouldn't have reported it

601
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,700
without knowing

602
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:54,980
whether the man

603
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:56,980
is really Xiao Chuhe.

604
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:58,860
That's right.

605
00:25:00,500 --> 00:25:00,980
Tell us

606
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:02,940
what happened in the Kingdom of Yushi.

607
00:25:03,660 --> 00:25:05,300
What are the chances of that person

608
00:25:05,860 --> 00:25:06,740
being Xiao Chuhe?

609
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,140
You are not qualified for this.

610
00:25:10,020 --> 00:25:10,860
You are not permitted

611
00:25:11,820 --> 00:25:12,380
to discuss

612
00:25:12,540 --> 00:25:13,660
the affairs of the princes.

613
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:16,340
Sir.

614
00:25:19,420 --> 00:25:20,260
Dozens of groups of people

615
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:21,900
have left

616
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:23,580
Tianqi City in the past year.

617
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:25,580
Where have they all gone?

618
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:29,420
They have gone to Xueyue City,

619
00:25:29,860 --> 00:25:30,500
Wushuang City,

620
00:25:30,860 --> 00:25:31,540
Muliang City,

621
00:25:32,060 --> 00:25:32,940
the Lei family of Jiangnan,

622
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:34,140
the Tang Clan of Shu,

623
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:35,940
the Wen family of Lingnan,

624
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:37,780
Mount Wangcheng, Mount Wudang,

625
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,500
Shaolin Temple, Yunlin Temple,

626
00:25:40,180 --> 00:25:40,940
as well as

627
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:42,660
the unreachable Tianwaitian,

628
00:25:43,300 --> 00:25:46,060
and Dark River that is nowhere to be found.

629
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:48,220
Yes.

630
00:25:49,260 --> 00:25:50,620
Both Lord Bai and Lord Chi

631
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:51,860
have sent men

632
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:53,380
to almost all the great martial arts sects.

633
00:25:54,260 --> 00:25:56,020
Now that the disputes in the court

634
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:56,860
have not yet ended,

635
00:25:57,500 --> 00:25:58,500
the rivalry in the martial arts world

636
00:25:59,180 --> 00:25:59,900
has already begun.

637
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:01,380
That's right.

638
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:02,860
You're right.

639
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:05,460
Jinyan,

640
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:07,820
did you just say you wanted to

641
00:26:08,580 --> 00:26:10,620
influence the name on the scroll?

642
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,460
My dear sir.

643
00:26:19,500 --> 00:26:19,940
Sir.

644
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:20,860
Sir.

645
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:23,900
I have made a slip of the tongue.

646
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:28,140
Good for you to know that.

647
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:33,860
I know

648
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:36,180
you each have

649
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:37,300
your own thoughts.

650
00:26:38,020 --> 00:26:39,100
But the Five Eunuchs

651
00:26:39,740 --> 00:26:41,660
shall be subject to His Majesty's will.

652
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:43,860
His Majesty's thoughts are unpredictable,

653
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,460
and we're like keeping a tiger company.

654
00:26:46,420 --> 00:26:48,260
If you are satisfied, you won't be humiliated.
If you know moderation, you won't be in danger.

655
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:50,060
In this way, you can live a long life.

656
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,860
If anyone can't understand

657
00:26:55,860 --> 00:26:56,860
this,

658
00:26:57,820 --> 00:27:00,780
you should quit being the Five Eunuchs
before it's too late.

659
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:02,980
Yes, sir.

660
00:27:14,340 --> 00:27:15,580
Although you have never made a choice,

661
00:27:16,100 --> 00:27:16,620
I know

662
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:18,380
you have always liked

663
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,420
the Sixth Prince, Xiao Chuhe.

664
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,740
Why must we make a choice?

665
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,580
These princes

666
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:27,060
were all good friends

667
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,020
when they were little,

668
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:31,060
and it is only because of our own interests

669
00:27:33,020 --> 00:27:34,100
that they have become

670
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:35,100
what they are today.

671
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:42,060
[Young Xiao Chuhe]

672
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:43,820
[Young Xiao Chong]

673
00:27:45,260 --> 00:27:45,940
My book.

674
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:48,420
Chong, I will get it.

675
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:52,020
Chuhe,

676
00:27:52,460 --> 00:27:53,340
be careful.

677
00:28:00,420 --> 00:28:00,980
Chong,

678
00:28:01,660 --> 00:28:02,620
you should stop reading.

679
00:28:03,580 --> 00:28:03,980
Look,

680
00:28:04,580 --> 00:28:05,300
the book is all wet.

681
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,980
Just play with me for a while.

682
00:28:07,820 --> 00:28:08,300
Chuhe,

683
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:10,300
you've been scolded by the school teacher

684
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:11,500
every day,

685
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,500
but you want me to be scolded too?

686
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:14,580
Chong,

687
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:16,210
actually,

688
00:28:16,540 --> 00:28:17,220
I can recite the content

689
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:18,420
of this book already.

690
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:20,900
I just want to piss off that old man.

691
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:24,740
Don't eat it.

692
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:27,020
Look, your hands are so dirty.

693
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:29,060
Go back and wash it before eating it.

694
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:30,060
All right.

695
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:42,420
Don't eat it!

696
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:43,380
Don't eat it.

697
00:28:45,820 --> 00:28:46,660
What should not be eaten?

698
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:51,420
Why are you here?

699
00:28:53,780 --> 00:28:54,780
I brought some snacks for you.

700
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:55,540
Here.

701
00:28:58,020 --> 00:29:00,100
Someone who is unaccountably solicitous
is hiding evil intentions.

702
00:29:00,420 --> 00:29:01,100
You have a favor to ask of me.

703
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:01,780
Say it.

704
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:04,660
Nothing, I just want to ask you something.

705
00:29:05,220 --> 00:29:06,540
What does the Prince want from you?

706
00:29:07,340 --> 00:29:07,980
Elder Yin said

707
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:09,140
you were classmates.

708
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:11,340
We just caught up on old times.

709
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:12,300
Nothing serious.

710
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:13,620
All right.

711
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:14,460
It's okay if you have secrets

712
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:14,940
to hide from us.

713
00:29:15,580 --> 00:29:16,900
If you don't want to talk about it, I won't ask.

714
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:18,740
Well,

715
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:20,020
the tournament of marriage

716
00:29:20,220 --> 00:29:21,100
is finally over for good.

717
00:29:21,540 --> 00:29:22,540
A big problem is settled.

718
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,140
Why don't we

719
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:25,820
go for a stroll in the city to take a breather?

720
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:27,780
Get to the point.

721
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:31,100
I haven't seen Miss Ye for a long time.

722
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:33,660
I'd like you to come with me to visit her.

723
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:35,780
Coward.

724
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,260
Go and see her yourself.

725
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:38,820
I'm too shy to do that.

726
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:41,780
She is a good friend of Sikong Qianluo.

727
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:42,820
You should find Sikong Qianluo for help.

728
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,140
I went to find Qianluo,

729
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:44,900
but she was not around.

730
00:29:47,300 --> 00:29:47,860
I get it now.

731
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:49,900
You came to me

732
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:51,100
when you were desperate, didn't you?

733
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:51,660
No.

734
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:52,980
Xiao Se,

735
00:29:53,020 --> 00:29:54,340
why don't you accompany me there?

736
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:55,540
Where's your sassiness

737
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:56,180
from yesterday?

738
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:58,660
We'll talk

739
00:29:59,020 --> 00:29:59,460
after you've finished these.

740
00:30:10,340 --> 00:30:10,700
Xiao Se.

741
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:26,060
The best taste of this Hongshan Zhuyan

742
00:30:26,340 --> 00:30:27,820
will be lost

743
00:30:29,100 --> 00:30:29,700
if it is cooked

744
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:30,580
a moment longer.

745
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,140
Greetings, Your Highness.

746
00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:42,300
Zang Ming and I are taking a walk in the city

747
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:44,460
and we suddenly smelled this tea scent.

748
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:45,860
I was wondering

749
00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:47,700
who in this Xueyue City

750
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:49,100
would like

751
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:50,780
to drink the tea of Tianqi City.

752
00:30:51,980 --> 00:30:52,780
I didn't expect

753
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,060
it would be you again.

754
00:30:55,660 --> 00:30:57,060
I hadn't been home for a long time,

755
00:30:57,540 --> 00:30:58,940
so I wanted to have a taste of home.

756
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:00,340
Your Highness, I'm sorry to have distracted you.

757
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:05,140
Aren't you going to invite me for some tea?

758
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:06,460
Your Highness, please have a seat.

759
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:12,900
Xiao Se.

760
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,300
Have you thought of a reason

761
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:15,340
for dragging me to see Miss Ye

762
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:16,580
in such a hurry?

763
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:17,940
What reason do I need?

764
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:20,060
We're just passing by

765
00:31:20,740 --> 00:31:21,420
and we're thirsty,

766
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:22,940
so we want a drink.

767
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:26,140
If you just want a drink,

768
00:31:26,620 --> 00:31:27,660
then you're in luck.

769
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:31,220
What do you mean?

770
00:31:32,410 --> 00:31:33,820
The finest Hongshan Zhuyan

771
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:35,780
brewed with melted snow

772
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:38,420
from Mount Cang,

773
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:39,980
the taste...

774
00:31:40,620 --> 00:31:41,380
I don't understand.

775
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:43,780
Right,

776
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:45,420
it's like cast pearls before swine.

777
00:31:50,460 --> 00:31:51,420
Great tea indeed.

778
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:54,020
Right, Miss Ruoyi,

779
00:31:55,540 --> 00:31:57,820
did you see Chuhe yesterday?

780
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:00,500
I did.

781
00:32:01,540 --> 00:32:02,820
But he seemed

782
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:05,020
a bit different than before.

783
00:32:08,540 --> 00:32:09,180
How so?

784
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:11,660
He used to speak

785
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:12,780
in a loud voice,

786
00:32:13,260 --> 00:32:14,220
beaming with joy,

787
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:15,820
as if he had

788
00:32:16,050 --> 00:32:16,740
absolute confidence

789
00:32:17,020 --> 00:32:18,180
in everything in this world.

790
00:32:19,300 --> 00:32:20,180
But now,

791
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:22,180
he has become much quieter and slacker.

792
00:32:25,540 --> 00:32:26,020
Yes.

793
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:28,540
Chuhe has changed a lot.

794
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:30,860
Did he tell you

795
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:32,580
where he'd been

796
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:34,420
all these years?

797
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:36,900
He said he opened an inn

798
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:39,220
in a place with green hills at the back

799
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:40,820
and clear water at the front.

800
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:44,980
Miss Ruoyi,

801
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,300
Xiao Se and I are passing by

802
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:47,540
and have come to ask you

803
00:32:47,980 --> 00:32:48,700
for a cup of tea.

804
00:32:56,820 --> 00:32:58,820
Miss... Miss Ruoyi,

805
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:00,900
I'm sorry to bother you.

806
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:02,100
Well,

807
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:03,420
spare the formalities.

808
00:33:04,940 --> 00:33:05,220
Sit down.

809
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,140
May I

810
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:13,340
know your name?

811
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,180
I am from

812
00:33:16,180 --> 00:33:16,940
Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect,

813
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:18,460
and I have just been accepted
as a disciple of Xueyue Sword Deity.

814
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:20,420
So you're from the Lei Clan.

815
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,700
Why don't you just tell him

816
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:23,700
your date of birth?

817
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:26,740
You're here too?

818
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:29,100
I'm just passing by

819
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:31,220
and would like to have a cup of tea with him.

820
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:33,460
No problem.

821
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:34,500
But

822
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:35,740
I'm a bit unskilled

823
00:33:35,740 --> 00:33:36,620
at brewing tea,

824
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,220
so I'm afraid I'm wasting

825
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:39,500
this fine Hongshan Zhuyan.

826
00:33:40,740 --> 00:33:41,620
It's all right.

827
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:43,180
I can't taste the difference anyway.

828
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:52,220
Mr. Lei,

829
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:54,060
aren't you afraid of getting burned?

830
00:33:55,220 --> 00:33:56,900
I practice a technique called Fire Infusion.

831
00:33:57,380 --> 00:33:58,980
The heat of this tea is nothing.

832
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:00,380
Miss Ruoyi,

833
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:01,100
one more.

834
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:03,100
I should pour you a cup of hot water then,

835
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:05,660
so as not to waste this Hongshan Zhuyan.

836
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:07,540
Xiao Se.

837
00:34:08,300 --> 00:34:09,900
I finished it at once

838
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:10,980
because I was thirsty.

839
00:34:11,540 --> 00:34:12,260
I know

840
00:34:13,140 --> 00:34:13,820
about tasting tea too.

841
00:34:17,180 --> 00:34:18,580
Miss Ruoyi told me

842
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:20,900
that she went to see you yesterday.

843
00:34:25,060 --> 00:34:26,860
Miss Ruoyi went to see you yesterday?

844
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:28,060
Me?

845
00:34:35,860 --> 00:34:36,420
Yesterday, Miss Ruoyi

846
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:37,820
also passed by my courtyard

847
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,060
and came in to have a cup of tea.

848
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:45,940
She asked me

849
00:34:45,940 --> 00:34:47,220
about Tianqi.

850
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:50,100
That's good then.

851
00:34:51,220 --> 00:34:51,860
Miss Ruoyi

852
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:52,980
is alone in Xueyue City.

853
00:34:53,700 --> 00:34:54,900
As a fellow from Tianqi City,

854
00:34:55,700 --> 00:34:57,060
you should take care of her.

855
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:05,460
(But...)

856
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:06,940
[Vermilion Bird]
(Why should I be the Vermilion Bird?)

857
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:08,580
(It sounds so girly.)

858
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:09,780
(I want to be the Azure Dragon.)

859
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:10,340
(No,)

860
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:11,620
(Azure Dragon is mine.)

861
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:14,580
(All right.)

862
00:35:15,220 --> 00:35:15,900
(It's just a code name.)

863
00:35:16,290 --> 00:35:16,820
(What's wrong with Vermilion Bird?)

864
00:35:17,220 --> 00:35:17,820
(Changfeng, look.)

865
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:19,380
(Lianyue got a tortoise,)

866
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,060
(and he doesn't complain.)

867
00:35:21,140 --> 00:35:21,860
(I want to beat you up.)

868
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:23,380
Father.

869
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:26,060
Father.

870
